sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as API Fastify
    participant Queue as Redis Queue BullMQ
    participant Worker
    participant LLM as LLM Groq
    participant DB as DB Postgres pgvector

    User->>Frontend: Send Message
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/chat
    API->>DB: Save User Message
    API->>Queue: Enqueue Job
    API-->>Frontend: 202 Accepted Job ID
    Queue->>Worker: Process Job
    Worker->>DB: Fetch Agent Context and User Facts
    Worker->>Worker: Generate Embeddings MiniLM-L6
    Worker->>Worker: Extract Last Assistant Message Only
    loop Tool Calling Max 10 Iterations
        Worker->>LLM: Send Context and Tool Definitions
        LLM-->>Worker: Tool Call Request OR Final Response
        opt Tool Called
            Worker->>DB: Execute Tool fetch_biometrics
            Worker->>Worker: Append Tool Result to Payload
        end
    end
    Worker->>DB: Save Final LLM Response
    Worker->>DB: Mark Job Complete
    Frontend->>API: Poll /api/chat/status
    API-->>Frontend: Final Chat Result
